name: Glitch House [00] by RodriguezArtt
description: Stuck to objects located all over the world, is a large series of hand drawn metal tape stickers depicting this and similar images. Each house, there to greet anyone that meets their gaze. Many are gone, painted over, or removed and forgot, but the homes that remain, wish you the best in life  and exist to remind us all that  home is where the artt is.    This is their 1st digital representation via NFT.  Here for Ever, for You.
